      "stickermule": {
        "url": "https://www.stickermule.com/",
        "title": "Sticker Mule | Custom printing that kicks ass",
        "schemas": [
          {
            "@context": "http://schema.org/",
            "@id": "https://fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/1zm67lm807",
            "@type": "VideoObject",
            "duration": "PT1M15S",
            "name": "How to order custom stickers",
            "thumbnailUrl": "https://embed-ssl.wistia.com/deliveries/448b20a0879d4d720936b79c773eb29e.jpg?image_crop_resized=640x360",
            "embedUrl": "https://fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/1zm67lm807",
            "uploadDate": "2016-12-05T19:40:01.000Z",
            "description": "Sticker Mule makes it fast and easy to order custom stickers, magnets, labels, and more.",
            "contentUrl": "https://embed-ssl.wistia.com/deliveries/de2c3137cf071352664876f4abdb5812398d53e9.m3u8",
            "transcript": "Aaron just launched his new startup. He's ordering a bunch of custom stickers for an upcoming event. Jess sells handmade products online. She's getting custom labels to make her packaging beautiful.\n\nAnd Brian's a designer. He wants the best quality transfer stickers for the hand lettering project he's working on. They're all using Sticker Mule. Why?\n\nWell first of all, it's really easy. You just pick the custom product you want, then select a size, and quantity. Aaron uploads a high resolution image of his design, Jess uploads a photo of her hand-drawn logo, and Brian uploads a vector image of his lettering. Each gets a proof within a few hours.\n\nThey can approve the proof, or request changes until they're happy. And with Sticker Mule's quick turnaround and free shipping, they all get their orders super fast. Aaron's stickers are a hit at the event, and give his new users a way to show off their support. Jess' new packaging helps her earn some five star reviews and more sales.\n\nAnd Brian's transfer stickers are exactly how he wanted them, and how his client wanted them. Guess who just landed two more projects. For the highest quality custom stickers, magnets, labels, and more, the best companies, do it yourselfers, and designers use Sticker Mule. Start your order today and find out why.",
            "potentialAction": {
              "@type": "SeekToAction",
              "target": "https://www.stickermule.com/?wtime={seek_to_second_number}",
